item.title: CVE-2023-49594|2024-08-02T22:01:25.924Z -- instipod -- duouniversalkeycloakauthenticator
item.description: An information disclosure vulnerability exists in the challenge functionality of instipod DuoUniversalKeycloakAuthenticator 1.0.7 plugin. A specially crafted HTTP request can lead to a disclosure of sensitive information. A user logging into Keycloak using DuoUniversalKeycloakAuthenticator plugin triggers this vulnerability.
